items.title: Video filmed by ICE agent who shot Minneapolis woman emerges
items.description: The clip shows the chaotic moments before gunfire rang out on a Minneapolis street.

items.title: X could face UK ban over deepfakes, minister says
items.description: It comes after government urged Ofcom to use all its powers – up to and including an effective ban – against X.

items.title: EU reaches South America trade deal after 25 years of talks
items.description: Some farmers in Europe opposed the deal, but the EU Commission said it had listened to their concerns.

items.title: US film stars Meagan Good and Jonathan Majors to become Guinea citizens after DNA tests
items.description: The pair join other US celebrities reconnecting with their African heritage and taking up citizenship.

items.title: Trump warns of more Nigeria strikes if Christians 'continue to be killed'
items.description: The US president made the comment after being asked if the Christmas Day strikes were part of a broader campaign.
